<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
        <main class="container">

            <section class="hero">
                <div class="hero-left">
                    <p class="label">Independent Apparel Brand</p>
                    <h2>Shirts built for real life.</h2>
                    <p class="lead">
                        We design premium cotton tees with modern fits,
                        durable construction, and timeless style.
                    </p>

                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/products" class="btn">Browse Products</a>
                        <a href="/register" class="btn-muted">Create Account</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-right">
                    <h3>What We Focus On</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Premium materials</li>
                        <li>Clean silhouettes</li>
                        <li>Seasonal limited runs</li>
                        <li>Consistent pricing</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="spotlight">
                <img src="/images/tshirt.png" alt="Featured shirt">

                <div class="spotlight-info">
                    <p class="label">Featured Product</p>
                    <h3>Classic Crew Tee</h3>
                    <p class="price">$24.99</p>
                    <p>
                        A soft ring-spun cotton shirt with reinforced stitching
                        and a tailored everyday fit.
                    </p>

                    <div class="product-features">
                        <div class="product-feature">
                            <p class="feature-title">Brand</p>
                            <p class="feature">GAP</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="product-feature">
                            <p class="feature-title">Pattern</p>
                            <p class="feature">Varied</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="product-feature">
                            <p class="feature-title">Availability</p>
                            <p class="feature">In stock</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="actions">
                        <a href="/products" class="btn">View All Products</a>
                        <a href="/register" class="btn-muted">Register</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="about-store">
                <p class="label">About Us</p>
                <h2>Shirts built for real life.</h2>
                <p>
                    3-Shirts was created with a simple goal â€” make everyday shirts better.
                    We focus on clean design, quality materials, and fits that feel as good
                    at the end of the day as they did when you put them on.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Instead of overwhelming you with endless categories, we specialize in
                    one thing: shirts. From minimalist essentials to bold graphic drops,
                    every piece is designed to be wearable, versatile, and built to last.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Whether you're dressing up a casual weekend or layering for a night out,
                    3-Shirts keeps your wardrobe simple, sharp, and reliable.
                </p>
            </section>


        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>